var misc = [{
   "t1": "<h1>Message from the President</h1>\n<p>Pakistan Cardiac Society is not only a community but is a family where one really feel that he or she is a part of growing cardiology network in Pakistan .The joy of the society is that you have this large group of the like minded peoples with a passion for cardiovascular disease and its prevention and who are willing to walk the extra miles for patients care.</p>< p > Mission of the PCS is to promote education and learning in the field of cardiovascular medicine and surgery due to the fact that academic pursuit is requirement of the day as it not only standardize the evidence based approach , does and dont&rsquo;s of the day to day management of cardiovascular problems but allows us to keep abreast of the new techniques .advances and happenings across the globe so that we can practice them appropriately in our country , that&rsquo;s why Pakistan cardiac society is focused to propagate the latest advancement in different fields of cardiology through dedicated mega events of annual conference and with its collaboration other organizations with in Pakistan and abroad like American college of cardiology , European society of cardiology , Asia pacific society of cardiology , Saudia cardiology society and emirates society of cardiology etc , ,socialization in these events is another aspect which is one the less important in our lives with day full of drudgery importance of recharging batteries of the life enhances our clinical skills and better care of the patients .</p><p>My wish for the future of the Pakistan cardiac society is that community continue going like it is now and continue to bring together all specialist working in cardiology from different countries and from different sub specialities with in caediology . The vision I have for the pakistan cardiac society is first to get even better connected with physician , allied professionals and patients over Pakistan, to promote soumd ,unbiased research , to creat solidatory among Pakistani cardiologists and to achieve horminization of caediology training.</p>"},
{"t2": "<p>47th Annual CardioCon 2017 The City of Hyderabad is honored to warmly welcome you on the occasion of 47th Annual CardioCon 2017. On the behalf of organizing committee" },
{"t3":"<p>Prof. Dr. Feroz Memon Convener 47thAnnual CardioCon Pakistan Cardiac Society (Local Chapter Hyderabad) One of the greatest challenges in medicine is the incorporation of information and knowledge in our practice. Education began with gaining information which led us to seek knowledge. This may be so and very optimistic as knowledge creates possibility of change and improvement in our approach. It can create amazing devices and techniques" }]


